genresAdvancedInfo.name: belgian death metal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Belgian death metal is a subgenre of heavy metal that originated in Belgium. It is characterized by aggressive guitar riffs, fast drum beats, and guttural vocals. The lyrics often deal with themes of death, violence, and horror. Belgian death metal bands such as Aborted and Leng Tch'e have gained international recognition for their intense and brutal sound.
